dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until FI-AR item clearing (days)",
    "FI-AR cleared after net due date (%)",
    "FI-AR cleared after net due date with discount (%)",
    "FI-AR cleared with discount (%)",
    "FI-AR cleared without offered discount (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AR items cleared") 
        	AS "Time until FI-AR item clearing (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AR items cleared after net due date") * 100 
         	AS "FI-AR cleared after net due date (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AR items cleared after net due date but with discount") * 100
        	AS "FI-AR cleared after net due date with discount (%)",
        AVG ("3 - Info - FI-AR items cleared with discount applied") * 100
        	AS "FI-AR cleared with discount (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AR items cleared without offered discount") * 100 
        	AS "FI-AR cleared without offered discount (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
